custom_fonts_yn.comment:
Default: No
<script type="text/javascript">
    document.observe("dom:loaded", function() {
        if($("pickpack_options_general_custom_fonts_yn").getValue() == 1){
            $$('.customise_fonts_and_colours_items').invoke('show');
        }
        else{
            $$('.customise_fonts_and_colours_items').invoke('hide');
        }

        $('pickpack_options_general_custom_fonts_yn').observe('change',function(e){
            if($("pickpack_options_general_custom_fonts_yn").getValue() == 1){
                $$('.customise_fonts_and_colours_items').invoke('show');
            }
            else{
                $$('.customise_fonts_and_colours_items').invoke('hide');
            }
        });
    });
</script>

min_qty_in_stock.comment:
For custom minimum stock levels for specific SKUs, set like this:
                                <br /> &nbsp; sku1,min-qty-in-stock-for-sku1;
                                <br /> &nbsp; sku2,min-qty-in-stock-for-sku2;
                                <br /> &nbsp; etc...
                                <br /> ** These products will show, even if not in an order **
